## Green's Principle Evaluation System

Monthly recalculation formula per stat:

```
new_stat = current_stat × K(role) + monthly_value
```

- `K(role)` — decay coefficient from `ROLE_DECAY_COEFFICIENTS` in `constants.py`
- `monthly_value` — fresh stat computed by AI (or provided manually)
- Result clamped to 0–100
- History stored in `stats_history` table

### Role Decay Coefficients

| Role | K | Equilibrium (if monthly=30) |
|------|---|---------------------------|
| Junior | 0.4 | 50 |
| Mid | 0.5 | 60 |
| Senior | 0.6 | 75 |
| Staff | 0.7 | 100 |
| Lead | 0.75 | 120 (capped at 100) |

### Key files
- `backend/constants.py` — `ROLE_DECAY_COEFFICIENTS`, `ROLE_REQUIREMENTS`
- `backend/app.py` — `_do_green_recalculate()`, `_apply_green_formula()`, GitHub activity fetch for dashboard
- `assets/js/api.js` — `monthlyRecalculate()`, `getStatsHistory()`, `getDecayCoefficients()`
- `assets/js/pages.js` — profile page UI for recalculation button + history
- `pages/profile.html` — Green's recalculation card + stats history card

